retacoro 0.0.3
==============
Large matrices (up to 1000 elements) now can be used.

* Rewrite the package with to use sparse matrices.

* Solve for the first row and column, as all the other table elements can be calculated from them given the log ratios


retacoro 0.0.2
==============

* Add proper documentation and vignette.

* Introduce function recover_table, for recovering the table from the log ratios.


retacoro 0.0.1
==============

Initial version. Rescaling of given matrix.
